headline: AvalonBay Communities, Inc. Announces Appointment of Conor C. Flynn to Board of Directors
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., November 10, 2025--AVALONBAY COMMUNITIES, INC. (NYSE: AVB) (the "Company" or "AvalonBay") announced today that Conor C. Flynn has been appointed to the Board of Directors. Mr. Flynn will serve as an independent director of the Company.
